# Copyright Requirements

## 1. Copyright Header Format

**REQUIRED**: Include copyright header at the top of every source file.

### C++ / Protobuf Files
```cpp
// Copyright <current_year> Tranxmart, Inc. All rights reserved.
```

### Python Files
```python
# Copyright <current_year> Tranxmart, Inc.  All rights reserved.
```

## 2. Rules
- Use the current year when creating new files
- Place copyright header before any other content (including `#pragma once` in C++)
- **REQUIRED**: Include exactly one blank line between copyright header and other content
- Use exactly this format - no additional license text required
